    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your judgment against a particular type of creature is particularly harsh.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Wis 13, judgment class feature.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Select a favored race from the ranger's favored enemies chart. Any sacred or profane bonus you gain from a judgment is 1 higher for attacks you make against or take from creatures that match the selected favored enemy.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>You can gain this feat multiple times. Its effects do not stack. Each time you take the feat, it applies to a different favored enemy.",
